quran[77]{c,v,t}:
  25,1,Nihayat mutabarrak(ba-barakat) hai woh jisne yeh Furqan apne banday par nazil kiya taa-ke saarey jahan waalon ke liye nazeer(darr sunane wali/warner) ho
  25,2,"Woh jo zameen aur aasmaano ki baadshahi ka malik hai, jisne kisi ko beta nahin banaya hai, jiske saath baadshahi mein koi shareek nahin hai, jisne har cheez ko paida kiya phir uski ek taqdeer muqarrar ki"
  25,3,"Logon ne usey chodh kar aisey mabood bana liye jo kisi cheez ko paida nahin karte balke khud paida kiye jatey hain, jo khud apne liye bhi kisi nafey (faidey) ya nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhte, jo na maar sakte hain na jila sakte hain, na marey (dead) huey ko phir utha sakte hain"
  25,4,Jin logon ne Nabi ki baat maanne se inkaar kariya hai woh kehte hain ke yeh furqan ek mann ghadat cheez hai jisey is shaks ne aap hi ghadd liye hai aur kuch dusre logon ne is kaam mein iski madad ki hai.Bada zulm aur sakht jhoot hai jispar yeh log utar aaye hain
  25,5,Kehte hain yeh purane logon ki likhi hui cheezein hain jinhein yeh shaks naqal (copy) karta hai aur woh isey subah o shaam sunayi jaati hain
  25,6,(Aey Muhammad) Insey kaho ke “isey nazil kiya hai usne jo zameen aur aasmano ka bhed (secrets) jaanta hai”. Haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh bada gafoor ur raheem(Forgiving and Merciful) hai
  25,7,Kehte hain “yeh kaisa Rasool hai jo khana khata hai aur bazaaron mein chalta phirta hai? Kyun na iske paas koi Farishata bheja gaya jo iske saath rehta aur (na maannay walon ko) dhamkata
  25,8,"Ya aur kuch nahin to iske liye koi khazana hi utaar diya jata, ya iske paas koi baagh (garden) hi hota jissey yeh (itminaan ki) rozi haasil karta”. Aur zaalim kehte hain “ tum log to ek sehar zadah (bewitched) aadmi ke peechey lag gaye ho”"
  25,9,"Dekho, kaisi kaisi ajeeb hujjatein (arguments) yeh log tumhare aagey pesh kar rahey hain, aisey behke hain ke koi thikane ki baat inko nahin soojhti"
  25,10,"Bada ba-barakat hai woh jo agar chahe to inki tajweej-karda cheezon se bhi zyada badh chadh kar tumko de sakta hai, (ek nahin) bahut sarey baagh (gardens) jinke nichey nehrein behti hon, aur baday baday mahal"
  25,11,Asal baat yeh hai ke yeh log “Us ghadi” ko jhutla chuke hain aur jo us ghadi ko jhutlaye uske liye humne bhadakti hui aag muhaiyya kar rakkhi hai
  25,12,Woh jab dur se inko dekhegi to yeh uske gazab aur josh ki aawaazein sun lenge
  25,13,Aur jab yeh dast o pa-basta (zanjeeron mein jakde) usmein ek tangg jagah thoonse jayenge to apni maut ko pukarne lagenge
  25,14,(us waqt insey kaha jayega ke) aaj ek maut ko nahin bahut si mauton ko pukaro
  25,15,"Insey pucho, yeh anjaam accha hai ya woh abadi jannat jiska wada khuda-tars parhezgaaron se kiya gaya hai? Jo unke aamal ki jaza aur unke safar ki aakhri mazil hogi"
  25,16,"Jis mein unki har khwahish poori hogi, jismein woh hamesha hamesha rahenge, jiska ataa karna tumhare Rubb ke zimme ek wajib ul ada wada hai"
  25,17,Aur woh wahi din hoga jabke (tumhara Rubb) in logon ko bhi ghair layega aur inke un maboodon ko bhi bula lega jinhein aaj yeh Allah ko chodh kar poojh rahey hain. Phir woh unse puchega “kya tumne mere in bandon ko gumraah kiya tha? Ya yeh khud raah-e-raast se bhatak gaye thay?”
  25,18,"Woh arz karenge ke “ paak hai aap ki zaat, hamari to yeh bhi majaal na thi ke aap ke siwa kisi ko apna maula banayein, magar aap ne inko aur inke baap dada ko khoob saaman e zindagi diya hatta ke yeh sabaq bhool gaye aur shamat zadah hokar rahey”"
  25,19,"Yun jhutla denge woh (tumhare mabood) tumhari un baaton ko jo aaj tum keh rahey ho, phir tum na apni shamat (punishment) taal sakoge na kahin se madad paa sakoge. Aur jo bhi tum mein se zulm karey usey hum sakht azaab ka maza chakhayenge"
  25,20,"(Aey Muhammad), tumse pehle jo Rasool bhi humne bheje thay woh sab bhi khana khane waley aur bazaaron mein chalne phirne waley log hi thay. Darasal humne tum logon ko ek dusre ke liye aazmaish ka zariya bana diya hai, kya tum sabar karte ho? Tumhara Rubb sab kuch dekhta hai"
  25,21,Jo log hamare huzoor pesh honay ka andesha nahin rakhte woh kehte hain “kyun na Farishte hamare paas bheje jayein? Ya phir hum apne Rubb ko dekhein? Bada ghamand le baithey yeh apne nafs mein aur hadd se guzar gaye yeh apni sarkashi mein
  25,22,"Jis roz yeh Farishton ko dekhenge woh mujreemo ke liye kisi basharat (khush khabri) ka din na hoga, cheekh uthenge ke panaah-ba-khuda"
  25,23,Aur jo kuch bhi inka kiya dhara hai usey lekar hum gubaar(dust) ki tarah uda dengey
  25,24,Bas wahi log jo jannat ke mustahiq hain us din acchi jagaah thehrenge aur dopahar (mid-day) guzarne ko umdah muqaam payenge
  25,25,Aasmaan ko cheerta hua ek baadal us roz namudaar hoga aur Farishton ke parey ke parey (rank after rank) utaar diye jayenge
  25,26,Us roz haqeeqi baadshahi sirf rehman ki hogi aur woh munkireen ke liye bada sakht din hoga
  25,27,Zaalim Insaan apna haath chabayega aur kahega “kaash maine Rasool ka saath diya hota
  25,28,"Haaye meri kambakhti, kaash maine falaan shaks ko dost na banaya hota"
  25,29,Uske behkaye mein aakar maine woh naseehat na maani jo mere paas aayi thi. Shaytaan insaan ke haqq mein bada hi bewafa nikla”
  25,30,"Aur Rasool kahega ke “Aey mere Rubb, meri qaum ke logon ne is Quran ko nishana tadheek bana liya tha (the object of their ridicule)”"
  25,31,"(Aey Muhammad), humne to isi taraah mujreemo ko har Nabi ka dushman banaya hai , aur tumhare liye tumhara Rubb hi rehnumayi aur madad ko kaafi hai"
  25,32,"Munkireen kehte hain “is shaks par saara Quran ek hi waqt mein kyun na utaar diya gaya? Haan, aisa is liye kiya gaya hai ke isko achhi tarah hum tumhare zehan nasheen karte rahein aur (isi garaz ke liye) humne isko ek khaas tarteeb ke saath alag alag ajzaa ki shakal di hai"
  25,33,"Aur (ismein yeh maslihat bhi hai) ke jab kabhi woh tumhare samne koi nirali baat (ya ajeeb sawal) lekar aaye, uska theek jawaab bar waqt humne tumhein de diya aur behtareen tareeqe se baat khol di"
  25,34,Jo log aundhey mooh jahannum ki taraf dhakele janey waley hain unka mauquf bahut bura (most erroneous) aur unki raah hadd darjah galat hai
  25,35,Humne Moosa ko kitaab di aur uske saath uske bhai Haroon ko madadgaar ke taur par lagaya
  25,36,Aur unse kaha ke jao us qaum ki taraf jisne hamari aayat ko jhutla diya hai. Aakhir e kaar un logon ko humne tabaah karke rakh diya
  25,37,"Yahi haal qaum e Nooh ka hua jab unhon ne Rasoolon ki takzeeb ki, humne unko garq (drown/duba) kardiya aur duniya bhar ke logon ke liye ek nishaan e ibrat bana diya, aur in zaalimon ke liye ek dardnaak azaab humne muhaiyya kar rakkha hai"
  25,38,Isi tarah Aad aur Samood aur ashaab e Rass aur beech ki sadiyon ke bahut se log tabaah kiye gaye
  25,39,"Aur un mein se har ek ko humne ( pehle tabaah honay walon ki) misalein dey dey kar samjhaya, aur aakhir e kaar har ek ko gaarat (destroy) kardiya"
  25,40,Aur us basti par to inka guzar ho chuka hai jispar badhtareen baarish barsayi gayi thi.Kya inhon ne uska haal dekha na hoga? Magar yeh maut ke baad dusri zindagi ki tawakku hi nahin rakhte
  25,41,"Yeh log jab tumhein dekhte hain to tumhara mazaaq bana lete hain, (Kehte hain) “kya yeh shaks hai jisey khuda ne Rasool bana kar bheja hai"
  25,42,"Isne to humein gumraah karke apne maboodon se bargashta(astray/behka/gumrah) hi kardiya hota agar hum unki aqeedat par jam na gaye hotey”. Accha, woh waqt door nahin hai jab azaab dekh kar inhein khud maloom ho jayega ke kaun gumraahi mein door nikal gaya tha"
  25,43,Kabhi tumne us shaks ke haal par gaur kiya hai jisne apni khwahish e nafs ko apna khuda bana liya ho? Kya tum aisey shaks ko raah e raast par laney ka zimma le sakte ho
  25,44,"Kya tum samajhte ho ke inmein se aksar log sunte aur samajhte hain? Yeh to jaanwaron ki tarah hain, balke unse bhi gaye guzre"
  25,45,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhara Rubb kis tarah saaya phayla deta hai? Agar woh chahta to usey daimi (constant) bana deta. Humne Suraj ko uspar daleel (sun its pilot) banaya
  25,46,Phir (jaisey jaisey Suraj utha jaata hai) hum is saaye ko rafta rafta apni taraf sameit-te chale jatey hain
  25,47,"Aur woh Allah hi hai jisne raat ko tumhare liye libaas, aur neend ko sukoon e maut, aur din ko jee uthne ka waqt banaya"
  25,48,Aur wahi hai jo apni rehmat ke aagey aagey hawaon ko basharat bana kar bhejta hai phir aasmaan se paak pani nazil karta hai
  25,49,Taa-ke ek murda ilake ko iske zariye zindagi bakshe aur apni makhlooq mein se bahut se jaanwaron aur Insano ko sairaab (quench thirst) karey
  25,50,Is karishme ko hum baar baar inke saamne latey hain taa-ke woh kuch sabaq lein. Magar aksar log kufr aur nashukri ke siwa koi dusra rawaiyya ikhtiyar karne se inkar kardete hain
  25,51,Agar hum chahte to ek ek basti mein ek ek nazeer (darr sunane waala) utha khada karte
  25,52,"Pas (aey Nabi) , ka firon ki baat hargiz na maano aur is Quran ko lekar inke saath jihad-e-kabeer karo"
  25,53,"Aur wahi hai jisne do samandaron ko mila rakkha hai, ek lazeez o shereen(sweet) , dusra talkh o shur (bitter and saltish), aur dono ke darmiyan ek purda hayal hai, ek rukawat hai(insurmountable barrier) jo unhein gud-mud honay se roakey huey hai"
  25,54,"Aur wahi hai jisne pani se ek bashar (Insaan) paida kiya, phir ussey nasab aur susraal (by blood and by marriage) ke do alag silsile chalaye .Tera Rubb bada hi qudrat wala hai"
  25,55,"Is khuda ko chodh kar log unko poojh rahey hain jo na inko nafaa pahuncha sakte hain na nuqsaan, aur upar se mazeed yeh ke kafir apne Rubb ke muqablay mein har baagi ka madadgaar bana hua hai"
  25,56,"(Aey Muhammad), tumko to humne bas ek mubashir (khush khabri dene waala) aur nazeer (darr sunane wala) bana kar bheja hai"
  25,57,"Insey kehdo ke “ main is kaam par tumse koi ujrat (recompense) nahin maangta, meri ujrat bas yahi hai ke jiska jee chahe woh apne Rubb ka raasta ikhtiyar karle”"
  25,58,"Aur (aey Muhammad) us khuda par bharosa rakkho jo zinda hai aur kabhi marne waala nahin, uski hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo,apne bandon ke gunaahon se bas usi ka ba-khabar hona kaafi hai"
  25,59,"Woh jisne chey (six) dino mein zameen aur aasmaano ko aur un saari cheezon ko bana kar rakh diya jo aasmaan o zameen ke darmiyaan hain, phir aap hi (qayinaat ke takht e sultanat) ‘Arsh’ par jalwa farma hua. Rehman, uski shaan bas kisi jaanne waley se pucho"
  25,60,In logon se jab kaha jata hai ke is Rehman ko sajda karo to kehte hain “Rehman kya hota hai? Kya bas jisey tu kehde usi ko hum sajda karte phirein?” yeh dawat inki nafrat mein ulta aur izafa kardeti hai
  25,61,Bada mutabarrak(ba-barakat) hai woh jisne aasmaan mein burj (fortified spheres) banaye aur us mein ek chiraag aur ek chamakta Chand roshan kiya
  25,62,"Wahi hai jisne raat aur din ko ek dusre ka jaanasheen banaya, har us shaks ke liye jo sabaq lena chahe, ya shukar guzaar hona chahe"
  25,63,Rehman ke (asli) banday woh hai jo zameen par narm chaal chalte hain aur jaahil unke mooh ko aayein to keh detay hain ke tumko salaam
  25,64,Jo apne Rubb ke huzur sajde aur qayaam mein raatein guzarte hain
  25,65,"Jo duaein karte hain ke “Aey hamare Rubb, jahannum ke azaab se humko bacha le, uska azaab to jaan ka laagu hai"
  25,66,Woh to bada hi mustaqar(evil abode) aur muqaam hai”
  25,67,"Jo kharch karte hain to na fizool kharchi karte hain na bukhl, balke unka kharch dono intehaaon (extremes) ke darmiyan aitadaal par qayam rehta hai"
  25,68,"Jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur mabood ko nahin pukarte, Allah ki haraam ki hui kisi jaan ko na-haqq halaak nahin karte, aur na zina (adultery) ke murtakib hotay hain. Yeh kaam jo koi karey woh apne gunaah ka badla payega"
  25,69,Qayamat ke roz usko mukarrar azaab diya jayega aur isi mein woh hamesha zillat ke saath pada rahega
  25,70,"Illa yeh ke koi (in gunaahon ke baad) toubah kar chuka ho aur iman laa kar amal e saleeh karne laga ho, aisey logon ki buraiyon ko Allah bhalaiyon se badal dega aur woh bada gafoor o raheem hai"
  25,71,Jo shaks toubah karke neik amali ikhtiyar karta hai woh to Allah ki taraf palat aata hai jaisa ke palatne ka haqq hai
  25,72,(Aur Rehman ke bandey woh hain) jo jhoot ke gawaah nahin bante aur kisi lagv (fizul/vain) cheez par unka guzar ho jaye to shareef aadmiyon ki tarah guzar jatey hain
  25,73,Jinhein agar unke Rubb ki aayat suna kar naseehat ki jati hai to woh uspar andhey aur behre bankar nahin reh jatey
  25,74,"Jo duaein maanga karte hain ke, “Aey hamare Rubb, humein apni biwiyon aur apni aulaad se aankhon ki thandak de, aur humko parheizgaaron ka imam bana.”"
  25,75,"Yeh hain woh log jo apne sabr ka phal manzil-e-buland ki shakal mein payenge, aadaab o tasleemaat se unka istaqbaal hoga"
  25,76,Woh hamesha hamesha wahan rahenge. Kya hi accha hai woh mustaqar (excellent abode) aur woh muqaam
  25,77,"(Aey Muhammad), logon se kaho, “mere Rubb ko tumhari kya haajat padi hai agar tum usko na pukaro. Ab ke tumne jhutla diya hai, anqareeb woh saza paogey ke jaan chudhani muhaal (never be able to avoid) hogi”"